  ## 1. Introduction
  
  ### 1.1 What is CloudSync?
  
  CloudSync Desktop is a powerful file synchronization application that keeps your files in sync across all your devices. Whether you're working from home, office, or on-the-go, CloudSync ensures your files are always up-to-date and accessible.
  
  **Key Benefits**:
  
  ✅ **Real-time sync** - Changes appear instantly across devices  
  ✅ **Selective sync** - Choose which folders to sync  
  ✅ **Version history** - Restore previous versions up to 90 days  
  ✅ **Offline access** - Work without internet, sync when connected  
  ✅ **End-to-end encryption** - Your data is secure and private
  
  ### 1.2 What's New in Version 3.2.0
  
  - 🆕 Smart sync technology (reduces bandwidth by 60%)
  - 🆕 Enhanced conflict resolution dialog
  - 🆕 Dark mode support
  - ⚡ 2x faster upload speeds
  - 🐛 Fixed: Memory leak in file watcher
  - 🐛 Fixed: Sync stuck on large files >2GB
  
