  ## 5. Core Features
  
  ### 5.1 File Sync Status
  
  **Icon Overlays**:
  
  - ✅ **Green checkmark**: Synced successfully
  - 🔄 **Blue arrows**: Currently syncing
  - ⚠️ **Yellow warning**: Sync issue (usually network)
  - ❌ **Red X**: Sync error (file locked or permission issue)
  - 📌 **Gray cloud**: Online-only (not downloaded)
  
  ### 5.2 Version History
  
  **Access Previous Versions**:
  
  1. Right-click file in CloudSync folder
  2. Select "CloudSync" > "Version History"
  3. Browse versions by date/time
  4. Click version to preview
  5. Click "Restore" to revert
  
  **Retention**:
  - Free accounts: 30 days
  - Pro accounts: 90 days
  - Business accounts: 1 year
  
  ### 5.3 Offline Access
  
  **Make Files Available Offline**:
  
  1. Right-click file or folder
  2. Select "CloudSync" > "Make Available Offline"
  3. Files download to device
  4. Access without internet connection
  5. Changes sync when online
  
  **Smart Sync** (Premium feature):
  - Files appear in folder but don't take space
  - Download on-demand when you open them
  - Automatic cleanup of old files
  
  ### 5.4 Conflict Resolution
  
  When two devices edit the same file simultaneously:
  
  1. CloudSync detects conflict
  2. Shows "Resolve Conflict" dialog
  3. Options:
     - **Keep Your Version**: Discard remote changes
     - **Keep Other Version**: Discard your changes
     - **Keep Both**: Save both as separate files
  4. Click choice to resolve
  
