  ## 8. FAQ
  
  **Q: How much does CloudSync cost?**  
  A: Free plan includes 5 GB storage. Pro plan ($9.99/month) offers 2 TB. Business plans start at $15/user/month.
  
  **Q: Is my data encrypted?**  
  A: Yes. Files are encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256). Zero-knowledge encryption available on Pro plans.
  
  **Q: How many devices can I sync?**  
  A: Unlimited devices on all plans.
  
  **Q: What happens if I delete a file?**  
  A: Deleted files go to trash for 30 days before permanent deletion. Restore anytime from web dashboard.
  
  **Q: Can I sync external drives?**  
  A: Yes, but drive must always be connected. We recommend syncing to internal drive instead.
  
  **Q: Does CloudSync work offline?**  
  A: Yes. Changes made offline sync automatically when reconnected.
  
  **Q: How fast is the sync?**  
  A: Depends on internet speed and file size. Typical uploads: 1-10 MB/s. We use delta sync for faster updates.
  
  **Q: Can I collaborate in real-time?**  
  A: CloudSync syncs files, not real-time collaboration. For live editing, use CloudSync Docs (separate product).
  
